<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-3"><a href="Purusha#Theistic_schools_of_Hinduism"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Theistic schools of Hinduism</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="Purusha#Varna_system"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Varna system</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-5"><a href="Purusha#See_also"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">See also</span></a></li>
