</li>
<li id="cite_note-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Purusha#cite_ref-10">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">A school of Hinduism that considers reason, as against <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nyaya" title="Nyaya">Nyaya</a> school's logic or <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/M%C4%ABm%C4%81%E1%B9%83s%C4%81" title="Mīmāṃsā">Mīmāṃsā</a> school's tradition, as the proper source of knowledge</span>
</li>
